STATE of North Carolina
v.
Gerardo SOLACHE. No. 420P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 11, 2006. Gerardo Solache, pro se. Robert Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State.

AMENDED ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 9th day of August 2006 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wilson County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 11th day of August 2006."
